{
  "stem": "5188.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, you know, the child's view of Paris-- and one thing I remember that she took us for lunch or dinner at some restaurant, which had a roof garden.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were on a roof somewhere, looking at Paris.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then, of course, they had funny toilets in France in those days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They didn't have regular toilets, like I knew from Germany-- where you had to crouch down low.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That was something that I had never seen before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So things were going pretty well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then, of course, there was the ship-- the boat-- the When we got on there, that was child's paradise.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I loved the idea of eating all our meals in that beautiful dining room, with the waiter taking care of us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were not the kind of family that ate out a lot in restaurants.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So, to me, the passage was absolute luxury.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was just very, very exciting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was very cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I remember a lot of people got seasick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "This was because there was some kind of a storm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they weren't even-- we weren't allowed on deck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "My sister and I sneaked up on the deck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And there was ice all over the deck, so we were sliding, you know, the way kids do on ice, and had a wonderful time until they chased us off the deck, because they were afraid we'd fall overboard or something.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were some.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were also people who were just-- you know, Americans were still traveling.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were mostly Americans on the boat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The food wasn't exactly what we were used to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was plenty of everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We thought orange juice-- that was a discovery.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We used to eat oranges.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we didn't have orange juice.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
